name: THESE DAYS
description:
Everything just gets complicated nowadays.
Just want to be at home but bored always haunts, wants to leave but is afraid of the virus.
Yes, but what can we do? that's what happened "these days" we can only comply with the existing protocol.
.
But calm down, there are many ways to reduce boredom at home. For example: working out at home, eating lots of fruit, or getting enough rest.
It's easy to do and there are many benefits (at least for yourself)
